    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; 5 Engine Service Manual - Dual Stage Turbocharger Assembly -
        Installation - Exhaust Tubing
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="1">
        <title>Exhaust Tubing</title>
        <figure id="f3900004" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figN15/N15008.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="502px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Exhaust tube assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Exhaust tube assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M10 x 30 high temp bolts (4)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger inlet gasket</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 50 bolts and M8 nuts (2)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 27 bolts (3)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 50 bolts and M8 nuts (2)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply anti-seize to four M10 x 30 and three M8 x 27 bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply a light coat of clean engine oil to four M8 x 50 bolts and M8 nuts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the exhaust tube assembly on the engine and install a new turbocharger inlet gasket
                between the turbocharger assembly and the exhaust tube assembly.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install four M10 x 30 high temp bolts securing the exhaust tube assembly to the turbocharger
                and finger tighten bolts.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new exhaust gasket between the EGR cooler and the exhaust tubing. Install three M8
                x 27 bolts finger tight.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install two M8 x 50 bolts and nuts securing the exhaust tube assembly to the right exhaust
                manifold and finger tighten bolts
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install two M8 x 50 bolts and nuts securing the exhaust tube assembly to the left exhaust
                manifold and finger tighten bolts
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
